reviews.review_text: best source Best copy of this show available on the archives right now. Worth a listen. At points its really sloppy and jerrys vocals are lazy throughout most of it. However, It's amazing how they can be so sloppy during help on the way and straighten it out before franklins tower, then pull off a pretty damn good lost sailor, st circumstance, and one of the better terrapin's. If only jerry didnt sound so tired.
